{
  "Subject": "We value your feedback: Startup India Workshop | Talk with Investors",
  "Body": "\u003C!DOCTYPE html\u003E\n\u003Chtml\u003E\n\u003Chead\u003E\n  \u003Cmeta charset=\u0022utf-8\u0022 /\u003E\n  \u003Cstyle\u003E\n    body {\n      font-family: \u0027Segoe UI\u0027, Arial, sans-serif;\n      background-color: #ffffff;\n      color: #000000;\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n    }\n    .container {\n      max-width: 480px;\n      margin: 40px auto;\n      background-color: #ffffff;\n      border: 3px solid #000000;\n      border-radius: 0px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .header {\n      background-color: #8B0000;\n      padding: 32px;\n      text-align: center;\n      border-bottom: 3px solid #000000;\n    }\n    .header h1 {\n      color: #ffffff;\n      margin: 0;\n      font-size: 24px;\n      font-weight: 800;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 2px;\n    }\n    .body {\n      padding: 40px;\n    }\n    .body p {\n      color: #000000;\n      font-size: 16px;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      margin: 0 0 20px;\n    }\n    .info-box {\n      background-color: #000000;\n      border: 2px solid #8B0000;\n      padding: 24px;\n      margin: 30px 0;\n      color: #ffffff;\n    }\n    .info-title {\n      font-size: 18px;\n      font-weight: 800;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #8B0000;\n      padding-bottom: 4px;\n      color: #ffffff;\n    }\n    .info-item {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\n      line-height: 1.4;\n    }\n    .info-label {\n      font-weight: bold;\n      color: #ffcccc;\n    }\n    .btn-container {\n      text-align: center;\n      margin: 30px 0 10px;\n    }\n    .feedback-btn {\n      display: inline-block;\n      background-color: #8B0000;\n      color: #ffffff;\n      text-decoration: none;\n      padding: 12px 24px;\n      font-weight: bold;\n      font-size: 16px;\n      border: 2px solid #000000;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 1px;\n      transition: background-color 0.2s ease;\n    }\n    .feedback-btn:hover {\n      background-color: #700000;\n    }\n    .footer {\n      background-color: #000000;\n      color: #ffffff;\n      padding: 20px;\n      text-align: center;\n      font-size: 12px;\n      border-top: 3px solid #000000;\n      letter-spacing: 1px;\n    }\n  \u003C/style\u003E\n\u003C/head\u003E\n\u003Cbody\u003E\n  \u003Cdiv class=\u0022container\u0022\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022header\u0022\u003E\n      \u003Ch1\u003E\uD83C\uDF9F Event Platform\u003C/h1\u003E\n    \u003C/div\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022body\u0022\u003E\n      \u003Cp\u003EHello,\u003C/p\u003E\n      \u003Cp\u003EThank you for attending \u003Cstrong\u003EStartup India Workshop | Talk with Investors\u003C/strong\u003E! We hope you had a great experience and gained valuable insights.\u003C/p\u003E\n      \n      \u003Cp\u003EWe would love to hear your thoughts and suggestions. Your feedback helps us and the event organizers deliver better experiences in the future.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n      \u003Cdiv class=\u0022btn-container\u0022\u003E\n        \u003Ca href=\u0022http://localhost:4200/bookings?feedbackEventId=11987\u0022 class=\u0022feedback-btn\u0022\u003ELeave Feedback\u003C/a\u003E\n      \u003C/div\u003E\n    \u003C/div\u003E\n    \u003Cdiv class=\u0022footer\u0022\u003E\n      \u0026copy; 2026 Event Platform. All rights reserved.\n    \u003C/div\u003E\n  \u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/body\u003E\n\u003C/html\u003E\n"
}